# Java test conventions

Follow `ai-kit/TEST_CONVENTIONS.md`.

- `@DisplayName("should ... when ...")` — lowercase start.
- Method names: `shouldReturnXWhenY` / `shouldThrowXWhenY`.
- Prefer flat tests; max one `@Nested` level.
- Use `// Given`, `// When`, `// Then` in non-trivial tests.
- AssertJ for assertions; Mockito when isolating collaborators.
